1
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:25,880
Are you leaving or not?

2
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:26,880
Why should we leave?

3
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:28,800
That's not how contracts work!

4
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:29,840
Cut the crap.

5
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,080
You leave when we say so.

6
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:32,920
You're being completely unreasonable!

7
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:34,200
Reason? With you?

8
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,080
Get moving!

9
00:01:35,080 --> 00:01:35,840
We're not leaving.

10
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:39,320
You signed the contract.

11
00:01:40,160 --> 00:01:41,600
There's no justice anywhere!

12
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,040
Hurry up, drag him out!

13
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:44,280
Move it! I won't go, no way!

14
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:46,760
Move! I said move!

15
00:01:47,320 --> 00:01:47,760
Hurry!

16
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:48,960
Right.

17
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,080
Get them! Get them!

18
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:52,720
Tear it down!

19
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:54,320
Hurry up!

20
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:55,320
Move!

21
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:56,480
This is straight-up bullying!

22
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:57,120
Get out of here!

23
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:57,920
What are you doing?!

24
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:58,520
Scram!

25
00:01:59,040 --> 00:01:59,720
Stay back!

26
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:35,640
You wanted to see me?

27
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:40,800
What made you come over here all of a sudden?

28
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,680
I wanted to cook you a meal.

29
00:02:43,880 --> 00:02:45,240
The pickled cabbage you loved as a kid.

30
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,200
Let you have a taste.

31
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,400
It's been a long time.

32
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,360
So today,

33
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,840
let me show you what I can cook.

34
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,040
Oh, right.

35
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:58,520
How were things on your end this morning?

36
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,160
Not bad.

37
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,880
Wang Hao and the others are keeping an eye on it.

38
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:08,880
I really don't get it.

39
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:11,440
You never wanted to work down there anyway.

40
00:03:12,440 --> 00:03:13,560
Why don't you just come back?

41
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,840
I'll find you a position at the company.

42
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:18,880
Your place is way too big.

43
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:20,640
Besides,

44
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,400
it wouldn't make any difference.

45
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:37,600
Too bland.

46
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,520
Pass me the salt.

47
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,640
That's too much.

48
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,040
Okay, okay, okay.

49
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,600
What happened to your hand?

50
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,280
Come on, boss, have a drink. Come on.

51
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:41,600
Boss! Boss! Boss!

52
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:42,600
Nobody move!

53
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:43,760
What are you doing?

54
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:44,800
Back off.

55
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:45,720
Step back.

56
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,400
Kid.

57
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:49,560
You've got guts.

58
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,880
What? Your brother stabbing me wasn't enough?

59
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,800
You want to avenge him?

60
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,520
Killing you would be too easy.

61
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:58,640
Plus, I'd go to jail for killing you.

62
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,080
Then no one would take care of my brother.

63
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:00,960
I'll wait for my brother to get out.

64
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:02,360
And let him take revenge himself.

65
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:06,160
If you don't want revenge,

66
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:07,560
then why pull a stunt like this?

67
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:09,800
You sure you won't kill me?

68
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:10,720
If you can walk out of here.

69
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:11,800
Spit it out.

70
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:13,440
What the hell do you want?

71
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,040
Give me a piece of land.

72
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,480
And give me a sum of money.

73
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,440
Let me work for you...

74
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,600
What do you mean?

75
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,760
Otherwise, we both die together.

76
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,720
I'm getting nothing anyway,

77
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:27,000
and my brother will suffer when he's out.

78
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:28,920
Better I get his revenge first.

79
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:30,320
Fine.

80
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:33,400
If you can walk out of here alive today,

81
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,360
then I'll agree.

82
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:35,280
How about that?

83
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,600
Call an ambulance! Save the boss!

84
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:10,960
You've never

85
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:12,000
told me any of this.

86
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:18,000
I put something in your jacket pocket.

87
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:19,400
Go take a look.

88
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:38,800
Your painting.

89
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,360
When I moved, I didn't take anything else.

90
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,920
Just this one thing.

91
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:47,080
Remember?

92
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,680
That grand blueprint on it,

93
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:49,920
you were the one who came up with it.

94
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:01,120
So you didn't take it as a joke.

95
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:09,280
Hungry, aren't you?

96
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,520
Let's eat.

97
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:38,480
You barely talk anymore.

98
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,960
Not like before.

99
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:44,040
You were even loud during meals.

100
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,720
The pickled cabbage turned out great.

101
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:57,280
This place is about to be demolished too.

102
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:00,560
Lin You.

103
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:02,640
It's time to let this place

104
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:04,720
become what it's meant to become.

105
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:26,800
Great General

106
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,720
Do you remember?

107
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,960
Back then, you yourself

108
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,679
chose that area in West City.

109
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,600
So Daji has to be torn down.

110
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:45,560
When?

111
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,240
In the next day or two.

112
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:24,480
Who is it?

113
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,280
Just a spam call.

114
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:30,520
Eat up.

115
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,600
I'm taking you to meet someone this afternoon.

116
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:34,880
Another time.

117
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:36,760
No, that won't do.

118
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:39,000
Have some more meat.

119
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:51,000
Lin You, you little brat.

120
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:51,960
Not even picking up the phone.

121
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:54,720
Who knows where he ran off to.

122
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,960
And old Wang's gone missing too.

123
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:03,960
Maybe it's better you just lie there.

124
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:07,040
Saves you from this whole mess.

125
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:12,880
Bro.

126
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:16,400
Is our family really falling apart?

127
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:41,560
Master

128
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:46,440
Liu Liu

129
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:51,520
Why did you lie to me?

130
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,480
Master didn't lie to you.

131
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:54,840
Liu Liu

132
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,240
Listen to Master.

133
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:58,440
You must never let

134
00:10:58,440 --> 00:11:00,560
that evil thought inside you lead you astray.

135
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:01,640
Liu Liu

136
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:04,800
I believe you're not that kind of child.

137
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:07,480
I know.

138
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:09,480
About Yaoyao's death...

139
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:11,560
Please.

140
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,320
Please.

141
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:15,360
Stop tormenting me.

142
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:17,080
Stop tormenting me.

143
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:19,200
Just kill me.

144
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:21,000
Just kill me.

145
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:31,400
Not yet.

146
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:41,280
How could I be hurting you?

147
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:44,560
I'm helping you.

148
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:49,800
Release

149
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,880
always takes time, you know.

150
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,760
Just wait.

151
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:02,480
Liu Liu

152
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:06,640
Someone's coming.

153
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:13,800
Liu Liu

154
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:28,960
Weren't we meeting someone?

155
00:12:29,640 --> 00:12:30,600
Why did we come here?

156
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,400
You'll find out soon.

157
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,560
Brother You

158
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:35,680
Your phone,

159
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:36,880
hand it over first.

160
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:06,640
Some things,

161
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:08,960
unless the protagonist tells you himself,

162
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:10,640
you just wouldn't believe.

163
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,040
Today, besides the one you're here to meet,

164
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:17,200
there's also someone you've wanted to see.

165
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:20,760
Lin You.

166
00:13:27,640 --> 00:13:28,560
Long time no see.
